  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <div class="about">
    <div class="about-prompt"><span class="ps">$</span> whoami</div>
    <p>10+ years building mobile, mainly Flutter:</p>
    <ul class="about-list">
      <li>multi-chain crypto wallet spanning 13 blockchains</li>
      <li>white-label SaaS platform behind hundreds of branded apps</li>
      <li>multi-exchange trading aggregator</li>
      <li>e-commerce app with limited-release drops and a few unusual features</li>
    </ul>
    <p>I've worked in big mobile orgs and led small teams inside them.</p>
    <p>What I actually care about: code the next engineer can read without asking who wrote it, shipping things that don't become someone else's emergency three weeks later, and a team that works as a single mechanism.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- EXPERIENCE -->
  <div class="section-title">Experience</div>

  <section class="project">
    <div class="project-meta">
      <span class="project-company">Ice Open Network</span>
      <span class="project-dates">Nov 2024 – Apr 2026</span>
    </div>
    <div class="project-role">Senior Mobile Engineer</div>
    <div class="project-skills">// Flutter · Dart · Riverpod · Freezed · Melos · Drift · React Native</div>
    <p class="project-oneliner">Cross-platform app — Nostr-based decentralized social network + multi-chain crypto wallet</p>
    <ul class="project-highlights">
      <li>Built multi-chain wallet covering EVM, Solana, Cosmos and UTXO families with a chain-agnostic send/receive pipeline handling gas, validator fees, memos, UTXO dust and SPL accounts</li>
      <li>Delivered swap/bridge engine integrating 4 providers with quote aggregation, slippage control and automatic fallback</li>
      <li>Local-first persistence on SQLite (Drift) for coins, transactions, NFTs and user data</li>
      <li>Contributed across 30+ feature modules in a Riverpod + Freezed + Melos monorepo; delivered feed, stories, communities, search, comments and reactions on the Nostr-based relay</li>
      <li>Participated in Flutter-to-React Native migration and native app improvements</li>
      <li>Led a sub-team of 3 inside a 14-person mobile group; raised baseline code quality through static analysis and code-generation practices</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="project-links">
      <a href="https://ice.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Website</a>
      <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.ice.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play</a>
